room_title: Escape room "Missing" by Xcape The Quandary in Tulsa
review: My daughter and her friends had a lot of fun doing the “Missing” room for her birthday! Owners are super nice and very accommodating, we will be going back!

room_title: Escape room "Missing" by Xcape The Quandary in Tulsa
review: We just did the Missing room and LOVED it! The clues were very well thought out and kept us thinking. We managed to escape in 45 minutes with a few clues. Can't wait to do more rooms here
